# Daily Discoveries™ Framework (T-016)

**Full document:** `docs/DAILY_DISCOVERIES_FRAMEWORK.md`

Daily Discoveries™ are **not** daily tips. Curated entrepreneurial insight — small, meaningful, immediately useful.

## Core question

> **"How will this make me think differently about my business today?"**

## Discovery Principle™ (all three required)

**Learn** — genuinely valuable · **Connect** — why it matters · **Apply** — immediate use

Missing one → not a Spark Discovery.

## Ten categories (rotate naturally)

Entrepreneur Stories · This Day in Business · Mental Models · Marketing Psychology · AI & Technology · Innovation · Customer Understanding · Leadership · Research Spotlight · Hidden Connections

**Type:** `DiscoveryCategory` in `lib/sparkDailyDiscoveries/types.ts`

## Structure rhythm

Remarkable Idea → Why It Matters → Business Connection → Personal Connection → Suggested Action → Related Experiences

Discovery **never stands alone** (T-014).

## Required spec fields

Category · capability strengthened · Brain personalization · Asset/Card/Builder/Guild links when relevant · Gallery only when exceptional (T-015) · reflection question · practical application

**Type:** `SparkDailyDiscoverySpec`

## Companion

Natural bridges — Observatory, business relevance, project similarity. **Never** "Here is today's tip." Shari test.

## Integrations

- **Observatory** — future becomes practical
- **Spark Cards** — curiosity → depth
- **Momentum Builders** — Discovery → practice when appropriate
- **Gallery** — exceptional transformations only

## EF

2–5 minutes · easy to read · memorable · curiosity — not overload.

## V1 note

`lib/companionEnvironmentIntelligence/dailyDiscovery.ts` = estate **hospitality ambience** (holidays, tea). **Not** T-016 entrepreneurial Discoveries product.

Also: T-014 Ecosystem Connection · T-011 Spark Cards · T-012 Momentum Builders · T-015 Gallery · Spec 100 Transformation.
